Ing '''Governorate ning Beirut''' ([[Arabic language|Arabo]]: {{rtl-lang|ar|محافظة بيروت}}, {{lang|ar-Latn|Muhāfazat Bayrūt}}) ing magdili-diling [[:en:governorates of Lebanon|governorate ning Lebanon]] a bibilugan na mu ning metung a distritu ampong metung a [[lakanbalen]], ing [[Beirut]], a ya muring kayang tungku o capitoliu, bukud king iti ing tungku ning [[Lebanon]]. 

Ing lualas na niting governorate, 19.8 km² (e la kayabe deng [[karulun]] o ''suburb''); lipat ning malati nang sasakupan a lugal, iti ing pekamaulagang labuad king [[Lebanon]] uling king actividad king economia, politica, cultura ampong sociedad.

